  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Micro macro farm is a small game designed to run while doing other stuff.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Start planting seeds and watching them grow on your small garden, keep growing the farm and get yourself some gnome helpers to keep your farm going while you are focusing on other tasks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Harvest and produce items to gain money and experience. Level up to unlock new seeds and machines.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >15 Seeds / Plants </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 Machines </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >26 Recipes </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Level progression </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Idle gaming</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PLANT SEEDS AND WATCH THEM GROW</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685810/extras/54d73f0ef6303b05cf22173043899041.poster.avif?t=1774370418\" width=640 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685810/extras/54d73f0ef6303b05cf22173043899041.webm?t=1774370418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685810/extras/54d73f0ef6303b05cf22173043899041.mp4?t=1774370418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >HARVEST YOUR CROPS</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685810/extras/e56d22c2e00308c2398a76e2bdd226d2.poster.avif?t=1774370418\" width=640 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685810/extras/e56d22c2e00308c2398a76e2bdd226d2.webm?t=1774370418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685810/extras/e56d22c2e00308c2398a76e2bdd226d2.mp4?t=1774370418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >COOK AND PRODUCE DELICIOUS FOOD WITH VARIOUS MACHINES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685810/extras/79e4734ffe799b45efb4d74a3b78e0d8.poster.avif?t=1774370418\" width=640 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685810/extras/79e4734ffe799b45efb4d74a3b78e0d8.webm?t=1774370418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685810/extras/79e4734ffe799b45efb4d74a3b78e0d8.mp4?t=1774370418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SELL PRODUCTS TO GAIN MONEY AND EXPERIENCE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685810/extras/b3c72d7d2083945379842d7ff28f6623.poster.avif?t=1774370418\" width=640 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685810/extras/b3c72d7d2083945379842d7ff28f6623.webm?t=1774370418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685810/extras/b3c72d7d2083945379842d7ff28f6623.mp4?t=1774370418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GET SOME HELP FROM SM